{"data": [{"id": "4742542", "title": "Cryptocurrencies: Bitcoin Skyrockets Toward $100K", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2138995594/image_2138995594.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Abstract bitcoin concept\" data-id=\"2138995594\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2138995594/image_2138995594.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2138995594/image_2138995594.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2138995594/image_2138995594.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2138995594/image_2138995594.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2138995594/image_2138995594.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2138995594/image_2138995594.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2138995594/image_2138995594.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2138995594/image_2138995594.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">koto_feja</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>This weekly update tracks some of the largest cryptocurrencies by market share: bitcoin and ether. While both are considered to be high-risk when it comes to investing, the two have foundational <a href=\"https://www.etftrends.com/crypto-channel/bitcoin-ether-differences-etf-investors-should-know/?__hstc=70317391.f852e6ed886f34a2df66ba87c3e83acd.1720606397823.1732773101589.1733468449464.54&amp;__hssc=70317391.1.1733468449464&amp;__hsfp=1669205919\" rel=\"noopener noopener noopener\">differences that investors should know</a>. We've also included</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2138995594/image_2138995594.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742542-cryptocurrencies-bitcoin-skyrockets-toward-100k", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 20:30:00"}, {"id": "4742671", "title": "PSQ Holdings: Not For The Risk-Averse Investor", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/162922472/image_162922472.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Ethics is underscored heavily in a document: morality has relevance!\" data-id=\"162922472\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/162922472/image_162922472.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/162922472/image_162922472.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/162922472/image_162922472.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/162922472/image_162922472.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/162922472/image_162922472.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/162922472/image_162922472.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/162922472/image_162922472.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/162922472/image_162922472.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">RapidEye</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>PSQ Holdings, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PSQH\" title=\"PSQ Holdings, Inc.\">PSQH</a></span>) is \u201cback.\u201d After our <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4638258-publicsq-ethical-e-commerce-contender\">last coverage</a> over a year ago in September 2023, and a \u201csell\u201d rating at a $9.42 stock price at publication, followed by a steep ~78% dip, dropping to a $2 low on November 18 (just two weeks</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/162922472/image_162922472.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742671-psq-holdings-not-for-the-risk-averse-investor", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 20:25:14"}, {"id": "4742670", "title": "Korn Ferry: I Struggle To See Upside Potential From Here", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192835/image_2155192835.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businesswomen meeting in lobby of modern office\" data-id=\"2155192835\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192835/image_2155192835.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192835/image_2155192835.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192835/image_2155192835.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192835/image_2155192835.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192835/image_2155192835.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192835/image_2155192835.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192835/image_2155192835.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192835/image_2155192835.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">MoMo Productions/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment action</h2> <p>I recommended a <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4719559-korn-ferry-macro-uncertainties-continue-to-linger\">hold rating</a> for Korn Ferry (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/KFY\" title=\"Korn Ferry\">KFY</a></span>) when I wrote about it on 6<sup>th</sup> September, as valuation has already recovered to historical average despite the macro situation</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192835/image_2155192835.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742670-korn-ferry-i-struggle-to-see-upside-potential-from-here", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 20:19:58"}, {"id": "4742675", "title": "The November Jobs Report Highlights Underlying Weakness In The Labor Market", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838283360/image_838283360.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Close-up Of Unemployed Businessperson Carrying Cardboard Box\" data-id=\"838283360\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838283360/image_838283360.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838283360/image_838283360.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838283360/image_838283360.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838283360/image_838283360.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838283360/image_838283360.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838283360/image_838283360.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838283360/image_838283360.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838283360/image_838283360.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">RUNSTUDIO</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>November Labor Report Highlights</strong></h2> <p>Earlier today, the Bureau of Labor Statistics reported the <a href=\"https://www.bls.gov/news.release/empsit.nr0.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">November employment report</a> for the US economy. The report indicated a better than expected 227,000 jobs increase in the month of November and a rare increase</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838283360/image_838283360.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742675-november-jobs-report-highlights-underlying-weakness-labor-market", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 20:15:33"}, {"id": "4742667", "title": "The December FOMC Fed Meeting And How To Play It", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172781953/image_172781953.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"The US Federal Reserve building in Washington DC\" data-id=\"172781953\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3000px\" height=\"2004px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172781953/image_172781953.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172781953/image_172781953.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172781953/image_172781953.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172781953/image_172781953.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172781953/image_172781953.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172781953/image_172781953.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172781953/image_172781953.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172781953/image_172781953.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">uschools</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>This article provides an impact assessment of the FOMC December meeting and a possible change in the Federal Funds Rate, whether it will go up, down, or stay the same, and what happens when it does.</p> <p>The chart below</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172781953/image_172781953.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742667-the-december-fomc-fed-meeting-and-how-to-play-it", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 20:08:58"}, {"id": "4742663", "title": "The Market Has Gotten Too Hot, Here's What I Would Do", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/497309419/image_497309419.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Bianca loves the fan.\" data-id=\"497309419\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/497309419/image_497309419.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/497309419/image_497309419.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/497309419/image_497309419.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/497309419/image_497309419.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/497309419/image_497309419.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/497309419/image_497309419.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/497309419/image_497309419.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/497309419/image_497309419.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Kei Uesugi/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>The market has been on an absolute tear in recent years, and 2024 has been no exception. This year has been great for US stocks, with the S&amp;P 500 Index (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPX\" title=\"S&amp;P 500 Index\">SPX</a></span>) now</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/497309419/image_497309419.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742663-the-market-has-gotten-too-hot-heres-what-i-would-do", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 20:03:21"}, {"id": "4742659", "title": "TLTW: Bullish Bonds? Then Avoid TLTW", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/118370564/image_118370564.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Blank Government Check\" data-id=\"118370564\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3456px\" height=\"2304px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/118370564/image_118370564.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/118370564/image_118370564.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/118370564/image_118370564.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/118370564/image_118370564.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/118370564/image_118370564.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/118370564/image_118370564.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/118370564/image_118370564.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/118370564/image_118370564.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">wsmahar</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The iShares 20+ Year Treasury Bond ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TLT\" title=\"iShares 20+ Year Treasury Bond ETF\">TLT</a></span>) has traded in a large range in 2024. After a large swing down from the September high, I think it can now recover and recently wrote an <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4740376-tlt-the-bessent-bottom\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4740376-tlt-the-bessent-bottom\" target=\"_b